47
00:03:15,708 --> 00:03:16,908
Looks good.

48
00:03:16,908 --> 00:03:18,907
In ancient times, 18 was the age of adulthood.

49
00:03:18,907 --> 00:03:20,168
People could make promises to the world

50
00:03:20,168 --> 00:03:21,428
