92
00:04:47,828 --> 00:04:49,888
Don't worry. Leave it to me.

93
00:04:49,888 --> 00:04:51,668
I'll make a perfect plan.

94
00:04:51,668 --> 00:04:52,688
However,

95
00:04:52,688 --> 00:04:54,948
