118
00:05:48,107 --> 00:05:49,387
Yes, let's eat first.

119
00:05:50,668 --> 00:05:52,068
Come on, learn it.

120
00:05:52,068 --> 00:05:53,547
Try this.

121
00:05:53,547 --> 00:05:54,656
Eat and learn.

